744
00:43:16,780 --> 00:43:18,880
Iaitu produk terbarunya.

745
00:43:19,160 --> 00:43:22,000
Semestinya luar biasa. Bersedia.

746
00:43:22,750 --> 00:43:25,290
Terima kasih banyak-banyak.

747
00:43:26,690 --> 00:43:29,020
Apa yang awak cakap ini?

748
00:43:29,200 --> 00:43:31,680
Sayang awak ada di sana...

749
00:43:33,790 --> 00:43:35,720
Adakah jus oren baik?

750
00:43:35,740 --> 00:43:38,110
Apa? Jus oren bagus.

751
00:43:38,140 --> 00:43:40,400
Jika boleh, tanpa seurat benang...

752
00:43:40,980 --> 00:43:43,630
- Maksud saya, dengan ais hancur.
- Beri saya sebentar.

753
00:43:43,650 --> 00:43:47,190
Slushie oren datang.

754
00:44:00,350 --> 00:44:02,690
Sudah selesai.

755
00:44:04,650 --> 00:44:08,550
Oh Tuhan. Dia tanggalkan pakaiannya.

756
00:44:08,570 --> 00:44:11,460
- Oh Tuhan.
