780
00:45:11,490 --> 00:45:13,090
Saya akan lindungi awak.

781
00:45:13,470 --> 00:45:14,870
Ingat?

782
00:45:14,890 --> 00:45:17,200
Saya adalah rakan niaga...

783
00:45:17,500 --> 00:45:18,900
