784
00:45:21,090 --> 00:45:22,490
Awak nakal.

785
00:45:23,610 --> 00:45:25,410
Jangan pernah khianati saya lagi.

786
00:45:26,410 --> 00:45:28,050
Jika awak lakukannya,

787
00:45:28,410 --> 00:45:30,040
awak akan mati.

788
00:45:31,010 --> 00:45:32,410
Tidak pernah.

789
00:45:35,170 --> 00:45:36,990
Oh, bagaimana dengan Ro Na?

