00:45:37,280 --> 00:45:38,680
Belum lagi?

791
00:45:39,570 --> 00:45:40,970
Tidak.

792
00:45:43,690 --> 00:45:45,090
Saya pasti...

793
00:45:45,690 --> 00:45:47,200
dapat jumpa dia lagi
suatu hari nanti.

